author: Aimée Lutkin
title: Rihanna Turned Twenty-Nine Today
text:
Image via Getty . 
Happy birthday, Rihanna. 
Twenty-nine is a strange age for many women. You haven’t yet crossed that mysterious threshold into your thirties, but your twenties seem definitively over. It’s tempting to offer every nugget of wisdom gleaned from more than three decades of living to someone standing on the brink of that change, but the fact is, Rihanna knows more than all of us.
